title: You’ve Been Framed | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: You’ve Been Framed | Joel Osteen
description:
Before you were born, God framed your life with a boundary of provision and protection. There is no mistake too great to keep you from His goodness and favor. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
